Arena = on-foot challenge (kart-blocking bollards), tune coins, add textures

- Bollard ring just outside the arena: a player squeezes between the posts but a
  (wider) kart can't pass or hop them, so arena coins must be grabbed ON FOOT —
  no more drive-through grabbing.
- Coins tuned down so it's a real challenge, not free money: value 300–1200 (was
  500–2500), 1–3 at a time every 9s (was 2–4 every 7s), expire in 16s (was 22s).
- Textures: metal panelling on the city towers, grass on the world ground, asphalt
  on the roads.

